DTSTAMP:20260319T022243Z
DTSTART:20260324T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Our March After Hours is shaping up to be one of the most uniqu
	e experiences we’ve offered. Join us on March 24th from 6:00–8:30pm as Sea
	ttle Makers opens their 12\\\,000+ square feet of creative space exclusive
	ly for our Chamber community. \\nYou’ll get a guided tour through their in
	credible maker environment\\\, explore the endless possibilities for hands
	‑on creation\\\, and watch live t‑shirt printing in action. Even better — 
	you’ll walk away with a custom t‑shirt you made yourself\\\, a fun reminde
	r of the night. \\nAlong the way\\\, you’ll meet fellow Chamber members\\\
	, learn the story behind one of our most innovative member businesses\\\, 
	enjoy a little pizza\\\, and experience the kind of creative energy that m
	akes Seattle Makers such a standout in our community. \\nThis special grou
	p experience is offered to members for just $40 per person — a significant
	 Chamber‑only discount. \\n👉 Reserve your spot and join us for creativity\
	\\, connection\\\, and community.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/ma
	rch-magnolia-after-hours-at-seattle-makers/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
