BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:m50XuwxguxnNDSfHpEtWh
SUMMARY:Reduced and Free Transit Fare Enrollment
DTSTAMP:20260319T022243Z
DTSTART:20260324T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:Low-income individuals and individuals with disabilities can re
