BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:BXOxb2Dj0IKB3A332Pia9
SUMMARY:Easter Celebration
DTSTAMP:20260319T022243Z
DTSTART:20260405T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Please plan to join MUCC on Sunday\\\, April 5th as we celebrat
	e Easter. This will be a joyous celebration with plenty of music and gift 
	bags for the kids and ending with a rousing rendition of the Hallelujah Ch
	orus! The MUCC Children’s Gathering Space will also be open on this Sunday
	 from 9:30 to 11:30 for all kiddos ages 0-5 of families who are attending 
	Worship Services. After Worship\\\, all of the young and young at heart ar
	e invited to the Easter Egg hunt outside and all are invited up to Pilgrim
